snippet.title: Scrap Arms - Kickstarter Trailer [Unfunded]
snippet.description:
The official Kickstarter trailer for Scrap Arms. A Roguelike RPG inspired by Mystery Dungeon.
The campaign launched in 2019, unfortunately it failed. But this isn't the end.

Play the demo now!
www.ernestplacido.com/scraparms

Trailer music arranged by LFOB:
https://twitter.com/zLFOBz
